					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1304786); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1304786&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164264" alt="TL333s" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1304786)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1304786); return false;" >TL333s</a></span> <span class="odate time_1394408049 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">09 Mar 2014 23:34</span>
